Code for exercise 11.5
----------------------

Description:
------------
ROOT macros for the measurement part.

How to run the code:
-------------------
root
[Example ROOT session:]
root [0] .L Measurement.C+    [compiles the code]
root [1] makeplots1()         [produces most of the plots]
root [2] run_pes()            [runs pseudoexperiments, writing results to a file

Files:
------
Pdfs.h          the PDFs for the two parameters for signal and background
Measurement.C   the macro for the measurement part.